column5: Do 50 pushups, 50 situps and 50 air squats as fast as possible
50 pushups,50 situps and 50 pullups - in that order
100 pushups, 100 situps and 100 airsquats as fast as possible
100 pushups, 100 situps and 100 pullups in that order and as fast as possible
For 15 reps each: hammer curls, standard curls, lying tricep extension, overhead press. Repeat in a circuit three times.
Do 10 burpees, then 9, then 8 etc. until you have finished in as little time as possible.
Do 25 burpees, then 24, then 23 in descending order until you have finished, as fast as you can.

4 exercises for 50 reps each with a moderate weight, 25lb dumbbells recommended: overhead dumbbell press, bent-over dumbbell rows, dumbbell bench press, renegade rows. Take as many breaks as you need.
Do a total of 20 clap pushups and 40 jump squats.
Do a total of 40 clap pushups and 60 jump squats.
Do a total of 60 clap pushups and 80 jump squats.
Perform the following yoga poses and hold them as long as you like: downward dog, child's pose, toe touches, twists.
Perform the following yoga poses and hold them as long as you like: downward dog, child's pose, toe touches, twists, crow, bridge, wheel.
Do 20 pushups, then 10 pushups, then plank for as long as you can.
Do 40 pushups, then 20 wide-grip pushups, then 20 tricep pushups.
Perform 70 pushups, then 30 tricep pushups, then 20 slow pushups (4 seconds up, 4 seconds down).
100 jumping jacks
50 jumping jacks, 20 high jumps (jumping off both feet as high as you can). Repeat 3 times.
50 jumping jacks, 30 high jumps, 20 bicycles. Repeat 3 times.
Two minutes of jump rope, rest two minutes, two more minutes of jump rope. Do at comfortable pace.
